{"word":"H1390 - גִּבְעָה - Gibʻâh - ghib-aw' - Gibeah","slug":"H1390","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גִּבְעָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Gibʻâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ghib-aw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Gibeah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>גּבעה</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>gib‛âh</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>ghib-aw'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Gibeah = \"hill\" <ol><li>a city in the mountain district of Judah</li><li>a city of Benjamin, birthplace of king Saul</li><li>a city in Kirjath-jearim of Ephraim</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H1389\">H1389</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1375\">H1375</a>, <a href=\"#/H1387\">H1387</a>, <a href=\"#/H1388\">H1388</a>, <a href=\"#/H1389\">H1389</a>, <a href=\"#/H1391\">H1391</a>, <a href=\"#/H1392\">H1392</a>, <a href=\"#/H1393\">H1393</a>, <a href=\"#/H1394\">H1394</a>, <a href=\"#/H1395\">H1395</a>, <a href=\"#/H25\">H25</a>, <a href=\"#/H4021\">H4021</a>"}]}